textAnnotations.description:
AFTER STATE PRISONS PROVED THEY WERE Too
STUPID TO CARRY OUT EXEGUTIONS, THE JOB WAS
OUTSOURCED TO ISRAEL
-. DEFINITELY
WE TOLD THE IDF
THERE'S A PALESTINIAN
CHILDREN'S HOSPITAL
A MILE AWAY.
DEAD
DIST. BY UNIVER SAL UCLICK.
8-11-I
